<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style> 
div {
  border-radius: 25px;
  
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  resize: both;
  overflow: auto;
  
  background-color: red;
  animation-name: example;
  animation-duration: 4s;
  animation-iteration-count: infinite;
  
  opacity: 1.0;
  
  float: left;
}

div:hover{
 opacity: 0.5;
}

@keyframes example {
  from {background-color: red;}
  to {background-color: yellow;}
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<p><b>注释：</b>动画，透明度，圆角边框，用户界面，浮动，伪类</p>

<div></div>

<p><b>注释：</b>动画会一直持续。</p>

</body>
</html>
